{"tid":1891100,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"演藝校友會譴責警方打壓創作","createTime":"2020-02-21T14:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T14:48:53.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"395ec0850eeb19ae8d758a009ccbe1fd1ee11ebf","tid":1891100,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T14:48:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200221/ENZEEDOLMMOHIAPCAUEFCNETI4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200221%2FENZEEDOLMMOHIAPCAUEFCNETI4%2F&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AABnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=49cc9799\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200221%2FENZEEDOLMMOHIAPCAUEFCNETI4%2F&h=2ec45d51\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200221/ENZEEDOLMMOHIAPCAUEFCNETI4/</a><br />\n<br />\n演藝校友會譴責警方打壓創作<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200221/large/1582206046_ae65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200221%2Flarge%2F1582206046_ae65.jpg&h=f750a1cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳詠燊任主席的演藝校友會撐《頭條新聞》，發公開信給鄧炳強表態。 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n上周播出的港台節目《頭條新聞》，因王喜參與的《驚方訊息》環節諷刺警方的工作表現，令警方發信予廣播處處長梁家榮表示不滿，而商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華，亦敦促港台必須遵守《香港電台約章》。前晚由導演陳詠燊為主席的「香港演藝學院校友會」發起，向邱騰華及警務處處長鄧炳強，發出一封譴責「警方打壓創作自由」的公開信，對於警方公然製造白色恐怖，表示真正的「極度遺憾」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，由一群香港電台節目顧問團成員包括莫乃光、邵家臻等，亦發起「香港人撐頭條新聞！促請廣播處長尊重編採自主，維護創作自由」聯署，前日開始讓網民簽署。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：翁可人"}]}